posting_body: ['Bring Your Pets!', 'Welcome home to Hawthorne Hill', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Hawthorne Hill Apartments', '11801 York Street, Thornton, CO, 80233', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 780 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'A NEW EDITION OF RENTAL LUXURY.', 'Hawthorne Hill beckons those who desire spacious living, a great location and luxurious amenities.', 'Exquisite finishes abound with nine-foot ceilings and crown molding accents, to optional cozy fireplaces and built-in desks.', "To make your life more enjoyable, we've included a fully equipped fitness center, resort-style pool and spa, and an elaborate clubroom.", 'Quick access to I-25 puts you within minutes of downtown and DIA is an easy drive away.', 'Features', '- Cable Ready', '- Balcony', '- Ceiling Fan', '- Garden Tub', '- Refrigerator', '- Fireplace', '- Washer & Dryer', 'In Unit', '- View', '- Microwave', '- Air Conditioning', '- Dishwasher', '- Oversized Closets', '- Garbage Disposal', 'Community Amenities', '- Business Center', '- Hot Tub', '- Individual Leases', '- Clubhouse', '- Public Transportation', '- On Site Patrol', '- Pet Park', '- Garage', '- On Site Maintenance', '- Extra Storage', '- Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog', '- Pet Friendly', '- Swimming Pool', '- Fitness Center', '- Playground', '- Emergency Maintenance', '- High Speed Internet Access', '- On Site Management', '- Accepts Electronic Payments', '- Wireless Internet Access', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly*', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'Rg4azEOgWTOc']
